05 Section

Kubernetes Pods

- Pod in Kubernetes is just the most basic unit of deployment.

- Pods are not visible outside the clusters


kubectl -> The most usefull command use in Kubernetes cluster

kubectl get all -> This command return all information from cluster

kubectl apply -f file-name.yaml -> This command is used to create pod inside cluster

kubectl describe pod POD_NAME -> This command is usefull to get all infomation from pod

kubectl exec POD_NAME ls -> This command is usefull to execute command against the pod, it's like an exec command from Docker.

kubectl -it exec POD_NAME sh -> This usefull command to get inside de container

